         The project consists of an IFC equity investment of up to US$5 million in Smartpaddle Technology Private Limited (Bizongo or the Company), a Mumbai based company that operates as a B2B technology platform providing one-stop-shop packaging solutions to medium and large companies. The Company curates, on-boards and provides access to SME packaging material manufacturers across India. The end-to end platform allows for strong customer and supplier stickiness and unlocks efficiencies in the supply chain.

